<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/190976-would-love-to-read-the-blind-owl-but-am">Would love to read THE BLIND OWL but am concerned about which English transition is best to start with. The D.P. Costello version seems the most readily available to me but have read that it might not be consistenly true to the text...any help would be appreciated.</a>
